<Layout title="AIA Pay Application Guide: How to Fill Out G702 & G703 | BuildWorkPro" description="Complete guide to AIA pay applications for subcontractors. Learn how to fill out G702 and G703 forms, schedule of values, and get paid faster.">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
